      "primary_method": "Callaway, Goodman-Bacon & Sant'Anna (2024) `did` continuous branch, applied cohort by cohort. With 2–9 treated units the `ATT(d|d)` level curve is the main estimand; the `ATT'(d|d)` marginal curve is rarely well-powered",
