      "chapter": "06-parallel-trends.html#sec-ife",
      "primary_method": "`fect` with interactive fixed effects (IFE) or matrix completion (MC). Latent factors absorb unit-specific trends and time-varying confounders that are correlated with treatment timing.",
      "alternatives": [
        "Synthetic DiD (`synthdid`) — unit and time weights soften sensitivity to time-varying shocks",
