        "Adequate pre-treatment span to identify the factor loadings",
        "No anticipation",
        "SUTVA: no spillovers, stable units, no hidden treatment variants"
      ],
      "caveats": [
        "Conditioning on observed time-varying X that is itself affected by treatment is a bad-control problem; latent-factor models avoid this by absorbing the confounding rather than conditioning on it",
